            <abstract>
                <p>
                    This is the long recension of the hagiography, attested in MS Ethio-SPaRe ADMY-014  
                    and possibly much more recent than <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1521GadlaY">Gadla ʾAbbā Yoḥanni za-Dabra ʿAśā</ref>. 
                    The work is subdivided into 12 monthly readings from 5 <foreign xml:lang="gez">Yakkātit</foreign> to 5 <foreign xml:lang="gez">Ṭǝrr</foreign>. 
                    <ref type="author" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1025Abaydo">Abaydo</ref> is indicated as the author in the prologue of the text. 
                    The text is part of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7156DossierYo">Hagiographical dossier on ʾAbbā Yoḥanni of Dabra
          ʿAśā</ref> and is followed by a <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7153MiraclesY">cycle of miracles</ref>.             
                </p>
            </abstract>
